Package: RegDDM
Title: Generalized Linear Regression with DDM
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Zekai", "Jin", email = "Jin.Zekai@nyspi.columbia.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    RegDDM fits generalized linear model where variables are estimated 
    Drift-Dissufion Model (DDM) parameters, using the Rstan architecture.
